author: danj
msg: Fix: empty SOAP bodies were not fully supported because isolation layers were not checking for null body
elements before trying to do things like type conversion or logging. Axis2 and JAX-WS can now handle
empty SOAP bodies, and the message handlers already take this into consideration.
